replies.body:
{{champion:83}} 

I agree that there needs to be a change to the turret system. Though I'd honestly rather see an overhaul rather than just a minor edit. Riot seems to treat the system like a frail pane of glass they'd rather not risk breaking, and for a number of reasons, I can see why. But with the ham fisted approach many players are able to get away with in order to push the game into their favor, the current turret system is laughable at best.

My last Yorick game? I took away 25% of an enemy's turret's hp away with one Q, thanks to the new rune system. This isn't URF. That should not be happening.
